            Tab Inactive FG:        [92, 92, 93]
            Tab Active BG:          [33, 35, 38]
            Tab Active FG:          [146, 146, 146]
            Tab Active FG L:        [37, 36, 37]
            Highlight:              [0, 172, 222]
            Modified:               [255, 0, 0, 48]
            Modified (HL):          [255, 0, 0, 163]
            Overlays:               [12, 12, 12]
            Tooltips:               [82, 82, 83]
            Match (QP):             [8, 140, 182]
            Match (SQP):            [8, 176, 222, 192]
            Puck:                   [0, 172, 222, 98]

            There may also be tweaked colors below where a subtle difference
            is necessary to get a small amount of contrast.
    **************************************************************************/

